name: Lights Shine Bright in America on the Square
description: This image, "Lights Shine Bright in America on the Square" was created with the assistance of artificial intelligence (AI). The concept behind this image was to reflect my first breathtaking close-up view of the bright lights shining throughout Times Square in New York City (USA). The process for creating this image included using a text prompt, algorithms, and artificial intelligence. The Snowpixel App was used in this process of creating this unique image. The image will be interpreted differently through the eyes and imagination of the viewer.
